<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234392>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7 – 12. Triraphis sicbaios, 7, head, dorsal view; 8, T. fasciipennis, ovipositor, lateral view; 9, T. fusciceps, ovipositor, lateral view; 10, T. ikelopsops ovipositor, lateral view; 11, T. simphlex, ovipositor, lateral view; 12, T. willei, ovipositor, lateral view. Scale bar in millimeters." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234392/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234407>
    dc:description "FIGURE 95 – 100. Triraphis willei, 95, dorsal habitus; 96, lateral habitus; 97, mesosoma, dorsal view; 98, mesosoma, lateral view; 99, head, anterior view; 100, metasoma, dorsal view. Scale bar in millimeters." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234407/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234409>
    dc:description "FIGURE 109 – 114. Wing venation and wing pattern for: 109, Triraphis ornatus (Cresson); 110, T. sicbaios; 111, T. paraholos; 112, T. simphlex; 113, T. prolixus, and 114, T. willei." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234409/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

